QuestData.Title: Warming Up
QuestData.Description:
We're nearing the island where the Horde's last expedition was lost.
You need to be prepared for what's out there. Warm up on these combat dummies.
Show me your strength!
QuestData.LogDescription: Warm up by fighting a Combat Dummy.
QuestData.CompletionText: Do not bother me! Go and attack those combat dummies. Show me your power.
QuestData.RewardText:
Good, you've kept training since we set sail.
I need to speak with the crew about this storm.
Spar with Throg. He will assess your skills and decide on your role once we make landfall.

Objectives.Objective: Practice combat on a Combat Dummy
